CATCH PSA
TO LONG BEACH
IT'S EASY TO GET IN AND OUT OF.
Avoid congestion. Excellent access via the
San Diego, Long Beach, San Gabriel River or Artesia
Freeways.
YOU GET FAST CAR RENTAL SERVICE.
Major car rental companies are right in the
terminal and their lots are just outside. No bus rides
or waiting to be picked up.
YOU GET ON-AND-OFF FASTER.
Faster boarding and de-planing. At Long
Beach. vou always board and de-plane through both
fore and aft ramps.
YOU FLY 727 SUPER FAN JETS.
All PSA flights to Long Beach are on 727
Super Fan Jets-the world's most popular airplane.
YOU GET CONVENIENT SCHEDULES.
From San Francisco, San Jose, Oakland and
Sacramento. And new service from Lake Tahoe.
See why more people fly PSA in California
than any other airline!
For reservations and information call:
SAN FRANCISCO - 761-0818
SACRAMENTO-922-8021
OAKLAND-568-4433
SAN IOSE-286-4720
LAKE TAHOE-588-5476
Or call your Travel Agent.
